    <briefdescription>
<para>A proxy loader for the file download plugin system. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>This class handles dynamic loading of file download plugins (e.g., curl-based plugin) and provides a static interface that matches the public file-download API.</para>
<para>Features:<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>Lazy loading: Plugin is loaded on first use, not at startup</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Graceful degradation: If plugin loading fails, function returns false</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Environment variable override: Can specify custom plugin path</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Thread-safe lazy initialization </para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
    </detaileddescription>
